import React from 'react'
import Carousel from 'react-bootstrap/Carousel'

import FirstPage from './First'
import SecondPage from './Second'

export default () =>
<Carousel interval={null}>
    <Carousel.Item>
        <FirstPage />
    </Carousel.Item>

    <Carousel.Item>
        <SecondPage />
    </Carousel.Item>
</Carousel>
